-- Great-West Awarded Loney C$4.44 Million in 2012, Filing Shows
-- B y   S e a n   B .   P a s t e r n a k
-- 2013-03-15T19:35:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-15/great-west-awarded-loney-c-4-44-million-in-2012-filing-shows.html
Great-West Lifeco Inc. (GWO)  awarded
Chief Executive Officer Allen Loney C$4.44 million ($4.35
million) in compensation, excluding pension-servicing costs last
year, the Winnipeg, Manitoba-based company said today in a
regulatory filing.  Loney was awarded C$4.12 million the previous year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sean B. Pasternak in Toronto at 
 spasternak@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
